WEBVTT

01:57.880 --> 02:00.560
You've finally come, my little brother.

02:01.520 --> 02:02.360
My brother, Chi Wen.

02:03.800 --> 02:04.720
I'm here.

02:07.000 --> 02:09.560
You are our long-awaited kin

02:10.600 --> 02:13.800
and the last hope
we have left for the world.

02:13.880 --> 02:14.840
What a pity.

02:15.880 --> 02:18.120
We won't be able to watch you grow up

02:18.200 --> 02:20.600
and transform into a dragon.

02:25.880 --> 02:26.840
I'm sorry.

02:28.280 --> 02:29.200
I'm sorry.

02:30.840 --> 02:31.840
For what?

02:34.680 --> 02:36.360
The last Dragon Deity's Power

02:38.040 --> 02:39.040
has dissipated.

02:40.720 --> 02:42.280
I can't be a dragon anymore.

02:44.280 --> 02:45.320
Besides,

02:47.240 --> 02:49.280
I still have fragments of Jiu Ying in me.

02:50.880 --> 02:52.960
He could manipulate me at any time.

02:56.680 --> 02:59.880
Perhaps this is fate.

03:01.120 --> 03:02.440
You can't turn into a dragon.

03:03.040 --> 03:05.040
But Jiu Ying can't kill me either.

03:06.120 --> 03:09.600
He is forever trapped in this dragon body.

03:11.680 --> 03:12.720
Is that it?

03:13.840 --> 03:15.440
You think I'll give up?

03:15.960 --> 03:18.720
Chi Wen. You're so naive.

03:37.640 --> 03:38.560
Chi Wen.

03:39.480 --> 03:40.440
Are you alright?

03:42.000 --> 03:43.000
I'm fine.

03:43.560 --> 03:44.800
Where's Ji Ling?

03:45.720 --> 03:47.520
Why didn't he come with you?

03:47.600 --> 03:49.720
He's the Dragon Deity we picked.

03:50.320 --> 03:52.000
I haven't seen him for a long time.

03:53.200 --> 03:54.280
Is he alright?

03:57.400 --> 03:59.120
Ji Ling is at the Shilin Sect.

04:00.840 --> 04:03.840
He was originally a little fox
at the foot of South Mountain,

04:03.920 --> 04:05.360
all carefree.

04:05.440 --> 04:08.080
But he swallowed
my dragon scale by mistake

04:09.080 --> 04:12.200
and shouldered a burden too heavy for him.

04:13.720 --> 04:14.800
I can see now.

04:16.440 --> 04:17.279
I can see now.

04:18.959 --> 04:19.800
What a surprise.

04:19.880 --> 04:22.600
The dragon scale didn't kill me

04:22.680 --> 04:24.280
and cured my eyes instead.

04:27.800 --> 04:29.000
It also surprised me

04:29.520 --> 04:31.840
that it was you, little fox,
who swallowed my dragon scale.

04:33.760 --> 04:36.000
Master Chi Wen, you remember me?

04:37.480 --> 04:38.800
Of course.

04:41.560 --> 04:43.440
Why did you swallow my dragon scale?

04:44.520 --> 04:47.320
I heard that it was a deadly mission

04:48.000 --> 04:50.000
and thought it would kill me.

04:50.080 --> 04:51.280
That's why I took it.

04:53.520 --> 04:55.040
He's a good man.

04:55.760 --> 04:57.600
I owe him my life.

05:02.400 --> 05:03.960
Maybe it was destined

05:04.800 --> 05:06.520
by heaven.

05:08.920 --> 05:09.760
Little fox.

05:11.360 --> 05:12.680
Do you have a name?

05:14.440 --> 05:17.560
From now on, let's call you Ji Ling.

05:19.720 --> 05:21.160
Ji Ling?

05:23.840 --> 05:24.960
Ji Ling.

05:27.040 --> 05:28.120
What a nice name.

05:29.680 --> 05:32.720
I have a name.
Master Chi Wen gave me a name.

05:37.200 --> 05:38.280
Master Chi Wen,

05:38.800 --> 05:41.800
does this name carry a specific meaning?

05:43.520 --> 05:46.560
I heard that names carry meanings

05:46.640 --> 05:47.520
in the mortal world.

05:49.680 --> 05:51.480
Whoever swallows my dragon scale

05:51.560 --> 05:53.960
becomes a vessel for my spirit.

05:54.960 --> 05:56.840
Ji Ling, a spirit vessel.

06:07.520 --> 06:08.680
Aren't you afraid?

06:14.040 --> 06:16.720
If you hadn't saved me,

06:17.240 --> 06:18.800
I would have died.

06:18.880 --> 06:22.160
Why would I be scared
to be your spirit vessel

06:22.240 --> 06:23.720
to save the world?

06:25.320 --> 06:26.480
I didn't expect

06:27.000 --> 06:29.960
that a little fox
could do such a great thing.

06:33.000 --> 06:36.080
So Ji Ling was a vessel for your spirit.

06:37.640 --> 06:40.800
Then why did you choose to stay here?

06:40.880 --> 06:42.480
Out of sympathy.

06:43.200 --> 06:45.600
Yuan Wuhuo was doomed.

06:45.680 --> 06:48.760
But Ji Ling showed up unexpectedly.

06:49.680 --> 06:53.320
I couldn't bear to take the life
of a kind creature at will.

06:54.000 --> 06:56.040
So we changed our plans.

06:56.120 --> 06:58.440
You made Ji Ling the "Dragon Deity".

06:59.480 --> 07:01.440
-Didn't you?
-Yes.

07:02.560 --> 07:04.520
No one needs to be sacrificed.

07:05.040 --> 07:06.400
I have another way.

07:07.560 --> 07:10.240
Just lend me your demon power.

07:10.320 --> 07:14.480
I have plans about how to regain
the Dragon Deity's Power.

07:17.040 --> 07:19.680
Greetings, Master Dragon Deity.

08:05.880 --> 08:08.160
I can't go on fooling around.

08:11.080 --> 08:12.480
It's time to grow up.

08:15.280 --> 08:17.400
Goodbye, little fox.

08:20.720 --> 08:21.880
I'll miss you.

09:18.560 --> 09:22.320
How come you're carrying
a fragrance out of nowhere?

09:23.720 --> 09:25.240
I bathe with only water
and eat vegetarian.

09:25.760 --> 09:27.520
There can't be a fragrance.

09:28.520 --> 09:29.760
There is.

09:29.840 --> 09:34.080
But this smell makes people sad,

09:34.680 --> 09:37.040
as if they're hollowed out.

09:43.800 --> 09:45.280
Autumn days are bleak.

09:45.360 --> 09:48.840
The golden-scale wood
is losing all its leaves.

09:49.680 --> 09:51.120
The branches look empty.

09:54.280 --> 09:56.000
That's why you have the delusion.

09:58.160 --> 10:01.600
If people can live for 100

10:02.920 --> 10:07.160
or 1,000 years, like trees,

10:08.800 --> 10:10.160
that would be nice.

10:20.680 --> 10:21.760
Not really.

10:23.160 --> 10:26.400
Trees are too lonely.

10:28.000 --> 10:29.200
For centuries,

10:29.840 --> 10:32.240
they had to stay put in one place.

10:34.840 --> 10:36.040
That's right.

10:37.560 --> 10:38.760
Little fox.

10:39.800 --> 10:43.400
You swallowed the dragon scale
and obtained immortality.

10:44.040 --> 10:47.640
But you're neither a human nor a demon,

10:49.840 --> 10:51.240
without a single kin.

10:52.600 --> 10:57.160
You became the loneliest outlier
in the world.

10:57.240 --> 10:59.840
Then you carry the gravest

11:00.640 --> 11:02.760
and most hopeless mission,

11:03.560 --> 11:05.960
trapped in this lonely courtyard.

11:08.160 --> 11:10.000
I'm sorry.

11:13.120 --> 11:14.440
I don't have kin,

11:15.680 --> 11:16.880
but I have friends.

11:18.520 --> 11:20.880
They are by my side, aren't they?

11:23.600 --> 11:25.080
But people around you

11:27.160 --> 11:29.360
will grow old one by one

11:30.280 --> 11:31.440
and perish.

11:34.400 --> 11:36.480
It's so cruel.

11:40.120 --> 11:41.920
You'll stay with me, won't you?

12:12.440 --> 12:14.080
My time has come, too.

12:20.360 --> 12:23.560
But the title of Dragon Deity
remains a faith

12:23.640 --> 12:25.440
as well as a huge burden.

12:27.080 --> 12:28.480
It's been a century.

12:28.560 --> 12:30.880
Things must have been hard for him.

12:32.640 --> 12:33.720
Has he changed?

12:34.800 --> 12:35.760
He…

12:36.280 --> 12:38.000
is somehow different now.

12:38.840 --> 12:40.960
He's no longer that simple little fox.

12:42.560 --> 12:44.440
His heart grew much heavier.

12:45.200 --> 12:46.400
His eyes were shrouded,

12:47.720 --> 12:49.160
impossible to see through.

12:50.480 --> 12:51.840
Is that so?

12:53.120 --> 12:55.080
That's why I came to see you.

12:55.960 --> 12:59.680
Ji Ling was haunted by his inner demon
and fell unconscious.

13:00.760 --> 13:01.600
Inner demon?

13:03.160 --> 13:04.240
Bai Ze said

13:06.680 --> 13:09.440
that it's a demon transformed
from your dragon scale,

13:09.960 --> 13:11.080
called Ji Can, the Lonescale.

13:12.240 --> 13:15.280
Sorry. I can't help Ji Ling.

13:16.080 --> 13:18.320
No one in the world
can defeat a Lonescale,

13:19.360 --> 13:20.960
except for Ji Ling himself.

13:21.480 --> 13:24.240
Because a Lonescale is also a dragon.

13:26.680 --> 13:27.840
Only dragons

13:28.960 --> 13:30.720
can kill a dragon.

13:31.240 --> 13:32.480
That's right.

13:33.520 --> 13:35.640
Destiny loves to play tricks.

13:36.200 --> 13:37.320
If I could

13:38.720 --> 13:41.480
trust him more and read his mind earlier,

13:42.360 --> 13:43.480
perhaps he wouldn't

13:44.600 --> 13:46.200
be controlled by his inner demon.

13:47.280 --> 13:49.440
He dressed up as the Dragon Deity.

13:49.520 --> 13:53.080
Since ancient times,
fancy attire has always been a shackle.

13:53.160 --> 13:57.640
My intuition tells me
that Wu Shiguang is not a bad guy.

13:59.560 --> 14:02.120
That low-rank weasel demon
only stole a gown.

14:02.200 --> 14:04.440
But he captured him for a reward.

14:04.520 --> 14:05.360
How is he not bad?

14:06.240 --> 14:07.880
He was trying to save that weasel demon.

14:09.240 --> 14:10.480
That weasel lacked cultivation.

14:10.560 --> 14:12.680
With his current level of power,

14:12.760 --> 14:14.400
he could only wear plain clothes.

14:14.920 --> 14:17.960
Silk and satin would be too much for him.

14:18.040 --> 14:19.160
He would die.

14:19.680 --> 14:20.840
I had no idea.

14:22.360 --> 14:25.160
Well then, your clothes are so gorgeous.

14:25.240 --> 14:26.960
Can you handle it?

14:54.880 --> 14:56.920
He wore the clothes of the Dragon Deity

14:57.800 --> 15:00.640
and had to put up with endless loneliness.

15:09.320 --> 15:13.000
I feel much better these days.

15:13.080 --> 15:15.520
I want to visit my hometown.

15:16.040 --> 15:20.200
My parents' tomb
hasn't been swept for quite a while.

15:30.560 --> 15:33.760
Aging and seriously wounded beasts

15:35.040 --> 15:38.400
always go alone
to the hidden caves in the forest

15:38.920 --> 15:42.640
at the end of their lives.

15:42.720 --> 15:46.520
They don't want their kin
to witness their death.

15:46.600 --> 15:50.240
That's their last pride.

15:54.880 --> 15:56.440
Stop looking for me.

15:57.720 --> 16:02.480
I don't want you to see my ruined look.

16:09.280 --> 16:14.040
Think of it as a final goodbye.

16:24.120 --> 16:26.120
I didn't achieve anything

16:26.200 --> 16:30.080
I've ever wanted to achieve

16:31.160 --> 16:34.200
throughout my life.

16:34.280 --> 16:36.400
I gained nothing.

16:37.880 --> 16:40.240
I failed as an older brother.

16:41.920 --> 16:43.520
Little fox.

16:45.040 --> 16:46.560
I have to go now.

16:47.960 --> 16:49.120
You shouldered

16:49.920 --> 16:52.880
so much burden for me in this life.

16:53.840 --> 16:56.040
I owe you way too much.

16:56.120 --> 16:58.880
I can't atone for my sins now.

17:01.160 --> 17:02.240
Child.

17:02.760 --> 17:05.520
You are kind and pure.

17:06.520 --> 17:08.480
But if there is an afterlife,

17:09.000 --> 17:13.079
I hope you can be selfish.

17:51.320 --> 17:54.000
It's getting cold. Let me grab you a gown.

18:47.800 --> 18:49.320
Master Chi Wen.

18:51.440 --> 18:53.320
My time has come.

18:55.960 --> 18:58.440
May I be so shameless

18:59.040 --> 19:00.720
as to ask you for one thing,

19:01.960 --> 19:03.280
please?

19:05.120 --> 19:06.120
I'm listening.

19:10.720 --> 19:12.280
For so many years,

19:14.360 --> 19:17.120
I've been by your side.

19:21.160 --> 19:23.720
I only see my wife and child

19:26.960 --> 19:31.880
on New Year's Eve.

19:35.640 --> 19:37.280
I take pride in my devotion

19:38.400 --> 19:40.160
to the Shilin Sect.

19:41.600 --> 19:43.320
However,

19:45.240 --> 19:47.120
I feel guilty to my family.

19:50.080 --> 19:52.040
My child wrote to say

19:54.760 --> 19:55.880
that his mother

19:59.640 --> 20:01.720
doesn't have many days left.

20:10.520 --> 20:11.480
You want me

20:12.760 --> 20:14.360
to save your wife?

20:14.440 --> 20:15.360
No.

20:16.760 --> 20:18.040
Master Chi Wen.

20:19.120 --> 20:20.480
I just want you…

20:21.760 --> 20:23.320
I just want you

20:25.520 --> 20:30.240
to grant me another day of health

20:32.480 --> 20:34.800
so that I have the strength

20:35.480 --> 20:37.360
to get out of bed,

20:39.320 --> 20:41.240
walk out of the Shilin Sect,

20:44.000 --> 20:45.960
and see her once again at home.

20:49.920 --> 20:52.480
Can you fulfill my wish?

20:53.360 --> 20:54.680
Master Chi Wen.

21:01.080 --> 21:02.000
I…

21:10.320 --> 21:11.480
I can't help you.

21:28.400 --> 21:29.440
I'm sorry.

21:33.280 --> 21:35.480
I overstepped.

21:36.000 --> 21:37.440
Master Chi Wen.

21:39.560 --> 21:40.960
The Dragon Deity's Power

21:42.040 --> 21:44.760
should be preserved
for those who need it more.

21:47.720 --> 21:49.680
I'll take one step ahead

21:51.960 --> 21:53.880
and wait for her in the other world.

21:57.760 --> 21:59.200
Master Dragon Deity.

22:00.840 --> 22:03.400
I'm so proud

22:05.440 --> 22:10.160
to be able to serve by your side.

22:45.280 --> 22:46.280
I'm sorry.

24:08.280 --> 24:09.160
Yuan Wuhuo

24:10.320 --> 24:11.240
died.

24:14.440 --> 24:16.600
Ye Daoxuan died, too.

24:21.560 --> 24:22.560
They both

24:27.560 --> 24:28.640
left me.

24:32.040 --> 24:33.760
I don't have the Dragon Deity's Power.

24:34.720 --> 24:35.960
I'm an imposter.

24:38.360 --> 24:41.440
I can't fulfill anyone's wishes.

24:43.320 --> 24:44.200
Nor can I

24:47.920 --> 24:49.680
keep anyone around.

25:16.200 --> 25:18.240
No one can keep me company forever.

25:21.960 --> 25:23.160
Maybe

25:27.160 --> 25:28.880
this will set me free.

26:25.560 --> 26:26.640
Don't be sad.

26:27.600 --> 26:28.640
Don't cry.

26:30.000 --> 26:31.840
I will always be with you.

26:36.120 --> 26:37.280
Don't be sad.

26:37.880 --> 26:39.120
Don't cry.

26:39.640 --> 26:41.400
I will always be with you.

