I will always be with you.

27:05.720 --> 27:07.200
-Wu.
-Don't be sad.

27:07.280 --> 27:08.480
Don't cry.

27:09.120 --> 27:11.680
-Is that you?
-I will always be with you.

27:13.080 --> 27:14.120
Wu.

27:16.120 --> 27:19.000
Don't be sad. Don't cry.

27:19.560 --> 27:21.160
I will always be with you.

28:03.640 --> 28:04.920
Who are you?

28:06.080 --> 28:07.520
I'm Lonescale,

28:08.160 --> 28:10.000
the loneliness residing in you,

28:10.080 --> 28:11.680
your inner demon.

28:13.120 --> 28:14.640
I am you.

28:22.000 --> 28:23.680
Lu Wuyi severed her spiritual tail

28:24.760 --> 28:26.080
and fainted from the pain.

28:26.600 --> 28:29.560
Her spiritual tail
corresponds to the eyes.

28:31.000 --> 28:31.920
What?

28:32.920 --> 28:34.040
Why did she sever her tail?

28:35.840 --> 28:37.720
She followed your soul

28:38.600 --> 28:39.960
back in time.

28:40.800 --> 28:42.800
To see everything,

28:42.880 --> 28:44.920
she had to attach herself to someone

28:45.960 --> 28:47.080
or something.

28:50.880 --> 28:51.880
Back then,

28:53.480 --> 28:55.320
I only had Yuan Wuhuo

28:56.200 --> 28:57.440
and Ye Daoxuan around.

29:00.240 --> 29:01.400
Who was she?

29:03.800 --> 29:05.960
Don't you already know the answer?

29:09.560 --> 29:10.600
Don't be sad.

29:11.600 --> 29:12.600
Don't cry.

29:13.880 --> 29:15.680
I will always be with you.

