29:47.680 --> 29:48.840
Don't cry.

29:50.000 --> 29:51.840
I will always be with you.

29:56.400 --> 29:57.480
My little fox.

30:03.120 --> 30:04.120
It was her.

30:06.960 --> 30:08.520
It's always been her.

30:13.720 --> 30:15.760
Let's reciprocate.

30:15.840 --> 30:18.920
Call me Wu from now on.

30:19.640 --> 30:20.600
Wu.

30:21.480 --> 30:23.720
The cry of a fox. Wu.

30:24.240 --> 30:26.560
It has the same name.

30:27.760 --> 30:29.520
It turns out that my Wu

30:30.840 --> 30:32.480
has always been my Wu.

30:41.240 --> 30:42.400
Master Daoxuan.

31:01.680 --> 31:03.000
Since you won't save him,

31:03.880 --> 31:04.800
you shall die too.

31:59.360 --> 32:01.480
It's so inconvenient to be a human.

32:04.040 --> 32:05.280
I can't even leave marks.

32:28.560 --> 32:29.600
Thank you.

32:42.200 --> 32:43.240
Here.

32:43.920 --> 32:45.000
Have some too.

32:47.480 --> 32:48.960
I left oil on your hands.

32:49.040 --> 32:51.440
It's fine. I'll wash you later.

33:14.800 --> 33:17.720
You are a little fox.

33:18.240 --> 33:19.200
You can't be furless.

33:20.120 --> 33:22.880
A bald fox will be mocked.

33:27.440 --> 33:28.920
I'll be hairless.

33:29.000 --> 33:30.480
Getting bald.

33:35.560 --> 33:38.040
I am a little fox without a name.

33:38.760 --> 33:43.000
But my little fox must have a name.

33:43.880 --> 33:47.120
Foxes cry like Wu…

33:47.200 --> 33:48.960
So I'll call you

33:50.320 --> 33:51.360
Wu.

33:53.880 --> 33:54.720
Wu.

33:54.800 --> 33:57.400
Wu.

33:58.280 --> 33:59.360
Yelp.

34:00.200 --> 34:01.480
Yelp.

34:01.560 --> 34:03.280
Yelp for me.

34:03.360 --> 34:04.560
Yelp.

34:06.200 --> 34:07.040
So naughty.

34:07.560 --> 34:08.400
I'll spank you.

34:08.920 --> 34:11.159
Yelp. Come on.

34:41.600 --> 34:42.800
It hurts.

35:01.920 --> 35:02.760
It hurts.

35:11.160 --> 35:12.840
I can't go on fooling around.

35:14.240 --> 35:15.720
It's time to grow up.

35:16.680 --> 35:17.600
Goodbye.

35:22.320 --> 35:23.840
I'll miss you.

36:39.200 --> 36:40.560
Don't be sad.

36:41.200 --> 36:42.200
Don't cry.

36:43.400 --> 36:45.240
I will always be with you.

