I will always be with you.

37:35.560 --> 37:38.400
Don't be sad. Don't cry.

37:41.960 --> 37:43.640
The past can't be changed.

37:44.480 --> 37:46.000
Trapped in this doll,

37:46.600 --> 37:47.960
she had to sever her spiritual tail

37:48.480 --> 37:52.080
and unleash all her power
to make a faint sound

37:52.160 --> 37:56.160
through that doll to stop you
from committing suicide.

37:57.400 --> 37:59.920
She is not only my moon,

38:03.000 --> 38:05.440
but she has also
always been my little fox.

38:30.760 --> 38:32.120
After that,

38:32.640 --> 38:35.520
you had a little talking fox
keeping you company

38:36.240 --> 38:37.680
and you were no longer lonely.

38:38.400 --> 38:42.160
You gave up the idea of suicide
and gathered the courage

38:42.760 --> 38:45.000
to become the Dragon Deity step by step.

38:45.920 --> 38:47.240
But the fox doll

38:48.080 --> 38:49.800
never spoke again.

38:51.640 --> 38:53.240
You told people about it,

38:53.760 --> 38:55.040
but nobody believed it.

38:58.200 --> 39:00.960
How can a rag doll comfort you?

39:01.040 --> 39:02.720
Don't tell me it can talk.

39:02.800 --> 39:04.280
It really talks.

39:07.200 --> 39:08.160
After that,

39:08.840 --> 39:11.840
you created Ji Ling
with the spell of Severed Silk.

39:12.360 --> 39:14.120
You gave him the little fox

39:14.200 --> 39:16.040
and sent him out to wander the world.

39:17.320 --> 39:20.360
Then he met Lu Wuyi.

39:21.440 --> 39:24.480
The universe is vast and exquisite.

39:25.360 --> 39:26.800
Even I find it hard

39:27.320 --> 39:29.280
to perceive everything.

39:30.240 --> 39:31.240
It turns out

39:32.840 --> 39:34.600
the beginning of the story

39:36.080 --> 39:39.600
has already been altered by Wu.

39:42.200 --> 39:44.000
Lu Wuyi once asked me

39:44.520 --> 39:47.040
why I would help her go back in time.

39:48.160 --> 39:50.880
I said I wasn't helping her.

39:51.480 --> 39:52.840
The person I wanted to help

39:55.040 --> 39:56.160
was you.

39:57.440 --> 40:01.360
Your ending was never
to die by your own hand,

40:02.200 --> 40:04.760
nor to sacrifice yourself to that drought.

40:07.160 --> 40:08.800
The end of your life

40:10.160 --> 40:11.560
has always been

40:13.920 --> 40:15.400
to be devoured by me.

40:18.280 --> 40:21.480
We must go back in time
to keep you from loneliness

40:22.480 --> 40:25.360
so that I never come to life.

40:26.640 --> 40:30.440
That is the only way to change your fate.

40:34.560 --> 40:36.920
Why would you sacrifice yourself

40:38.480 --> 40:39.760
to save me?

40:41.520 --> 40:43.600
Because you are a kind person.

40:44.600 --> 40:45.960
But for a hundred years,

40:46.760 --> 40:48.960
no one in this world has truly loved you

40:50.280 --> 40:51.880
or been willing to die for you.

40:52.960 --> 40:55.840
Is there anyone who loves you enough
to die for you?

40:58.320 --> 40:59.160
Is there?

41:04.120 --> 41:05.440
Now there is.

41:06.920 --> 41:07.960
She loves you enough

41:09.120 --> 41:10.680
to die for you.

41:12.800 --> 41:16.040
So, I should disappear.

41:17.120 --> 41:20.360
But the ending is written.

41:21.480 --> 41:24.520
This is too cruel for you.

41:27.400 --> 41:29.200
She only exists

41:30.200 --> 41:31.680
because of Jiu Ying.

41:32.680 --> 41:35.800
Once Jiu Ying dies, she will also perish.

41:37.880 --> 41:39.680
But the meaning of your existence

41:40.920 --> 41:43.080
is to annihilate Jiu Ying.

41:45.480 --> 41:47.960
The last Dragon Deity's Power
in this world

41:49.240 --> 41:50.720
has been destroyed.

41:53.640 --> 41:54.920
I don't have

41:56.880 --> 41:58.680
to reach the end.

41:58.760 --> 42:00.680
I used to be a dragon scale.

42:00.760 --> 42:01.800
Therefore,

42:01.880 --> 42:05.920
I carry the last Dragon Deity's Power
in this world.

42:07.600 --> 42:09.480
You can use it to kill Jiu Ying

42:10.000 --> 42:11.880
or to save Lu Wuyi.

42:12.680 --> 42:14.400
This final decision

42:16.520 --> 42:18.360
is up to you.

42:19.200 --> 42:21.440
Jiu Ying sent her to you

42:22.320 --> 42:24.640
to make you fall in love with her

42:25.720 --> 42:27.840
so that you would struggle

42:27.920 --> 42:30.160
between love and duty.

42:33.680 --> 42:35.760
This is what it means to be the fated one.

42:38.160 --> 42:39.440
Between you and her,

42:41.440 --> 42:43.440
one must live,

42:44.560 --> 42:45.800
and one shall perish.

43:17.440 --> 43:18.280
Commander Li.

43:19.120 --> 43:21.160
It's so late. Why are you here?

43:21.920 --> 43:23.400
I want to see Master Dragon Deity.

43:25.800 --> 43:28.040
Master Dragon Deity is in the Scale Cave.

43:28.800 --> 43:30.480
Go ahead, please.

44:03.680 --> 44:09.800
I won't let you hurt Master Dragon Deity.

44:10.520 --> 44:14.480
You are just like your grandfather,
Ye Daoxuan.

44:15.080 --> 44:18.760
You'd protect him
at the cost of your lives.

45:06.480 --> 45:07.520
Why did you come here?

45:10.760 --> 45:12.000
To kill him.

45:13.120 --> 45:16.120
The fourth Dragon Deity's Power
has been destroyed.

45:17.280 --> 45:19.960
Wu Shiguang can never
transform into a dragon.

45:20.480 --> 45:24.920
And Ji Ling will remain a false deity,

45:26.360 --> 45:28.200
suffering loneliness forever.

45:29.520 --> 45:31.720
What a cruel fate.

45:32.680 --> 45:35.040
I must set him free.

45:47.640 --> 45:50.280
Triple-flower paints the day.
All things live and perish.

45:50.800 --> 45:52.520
Before me, all becomes clear.

45:56.200 --> 45:57.320
Break!

46:16.960 --> 46:22.400
You're actually using the demon power
preserved for the inner core.

46:23.640 --> 46:25.040
Do you have a death wish?

46:26.320 --> 46:27.560
My life is yours.

46:28.680 --> 46:29.720
But he

46:31.480 --> 46:33.120
must remain alive.

48:17.400 --> 48:18.400
Bai Ze.

48:18.480 --> 48:21.920
Do you think you can beat me
with your petty tricks?

48:27.240 --> 48:29.320
Ye Changsheng. Well done.

48:35.080 --> 48:36.560
What did you do?

48:37.400 --> 48:39.400
Take my Purple Lightning Chain.

48:40.520 --> 48:44.680
If you see Yuan Wuhuo,
find a way to merge this with his blade.

48:53.640 --> 48:55.200
Young men of the Shilin Sect

48:56.320 --> 48:59.320
use faith as shields and courage as spears

48:59.400 --> 49:01.240
to protect the Dragon Deity and the world

49:01.840 --> 49:03.360
until the last minute.

49:04.440 --> 49:05.520
Ye Daoxuan.

49:07.600 --> 49:08.840
Ye Mingshan.

49:10.280 --> 49:11.480
Ye Changsheng.

49:14.520 --> 49:16.760
The devotion to the Shilin Sect lives on.

49:18.200 --> 49:20.520
Thus, light and hope
will never leave this world.

49:22.320 --> 49:23.400
Yuan Wuhuo.

49:24.560 --> 49:25.600
Your sins

49:26.440 --> 49:28.400
end with me today.

51:14.560 --> 51:15.840
Little fox.

51:18.200 --> 51:19.400
I have to go.

51:21.160 --> 51:22.760
I hope you don't

51:25.160 --> 51:26.640
feel lonely again.

51:59.440 --> 52:00.720
The fifth gem.

52:02.920 --> 52:03.960
Ji Can, the Lonescale.
